  "instructions": [
    "Wash and dice cucumber, avocado, and tofu into bite‑size cubes.",
    "Whisk Greek yogurt, miso paste, lime juice, orange juice, olive oil, and chili powder until smooth.",
    "Fold the diced vegetables and tofu into the yogurt mixture, ensuring even coating.",
    "Add chopped cilantro and minced red onion, stirring gently.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning with salt or extra lime if desired.",
    "Refrigerate the ceviche for 10 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve chilled over a bed of fresh lettuce or crumbled crackers.",
    "Garnish with extra cilantro or lime wedges for a romantic touch."
